snippet.title: Shape Up - E3 2014 Announce Trailer [NORTH AMERICA]
snippet.description:
SHAPE UP is the new fitness game coming for Xbox One in November 2014.
#ShapeUp
www.ShapeUpGame.com
 
You wanna stay in shape? Good news, getting fit just got fun.
Here's the idea: when you're having fun, you get a better workout because you work harder.
Every workout is a game- squat to the moon, vaporize aliens, and even doing push-ups with elephants on your back.
Try SHAPE UP yourself. Games that get you fit.  

Join us on Facebook: http://facebook.com/ShapeUpOfficial
Follow us on Twitter: http://twitter.com/ShapeUpGame
Follow us on Instagram: http://instagram.com/ShapeUpGame
